# TASK_PACKET

Task ID
CRUSHR-FORMAT-14A

Title
Add dictionary-target corruption scenarios and validate dictionary placement resilience

Role
BUILDER

Objective
Extend the deterministic corruption harness with bounded dictionary-target corruption scenarios, then compare dictionary-based identity variants to determine whether single-copy and header+tail dictionary strategies behave correctly and fail closed under direct dictionary damage.

This packet exists because FORMAT-13 showed that dictionary-based identity variants preserve full named recovery while materially reducing archive size relative to inline path identity, but the current harness does not directly target dictionary regions.

The goal is to verify resilience and fail-closed behavior when dictionary structures themselves are damaged.

